0.woff2" as="font" type="font/woff2" crossorigin="anonymous" data-next-head=""/><link rel="preload" href="/_next/static/media/Boyrun-Regular.woff2" as="font" type="font/woff2" crossorigin="anonymous" data-next-head=""/><link rel="preload" href="https://www.facebook.com/tr?id=792405807634160&amp;ev=PageView&amp;noscript=1" as="image" data-next-head=""/><script type="application/ld+json" data-next-head="">{"@type":"Organization","@context":"https://schema.org","url":"https://www.meetup.com/aws-user-group-lancashire/","name":"Meetup","logo":"https://secure.meetupstatic.com/next/images/general/m_redesign_630x630.png","sameAs":["https://www.facebook.com/meetup/","https://twitter.com/Meetup/","https://www.youtube.com/meetup","https://www.instagram.com/meetup/"]}</script><meta name="description" content="Welcome to AWS User Group Lancashire! This community welcomes anyone enthusiastic about Amazon Web Services (AWS), cloud computing or technology in general, whether you&#x27;re an experienced user or just starting out.Our aim is to bring together developers, architects, SysOps professionals, business lea" data-next-head=""/><meta property="fb:app_id" content="2403839689" data-next-head=""/><meta property="og:site_name" content="Meetup" data-next-head=""/><meta property="og:type" content="article" data-next-head=""/><meta property="og:title" content="AWS User Group Lancashire | Meetup" data-next-head=""/><meta property="og:description" content="Welcome to AWS User Group Lancashire! This community welcomes anyone enthusiastic about Amazon Web Services (AWS), cloud computing or technology in general, whether you&#x27;re an experienced user or just starting out.Our aim is to bring together developers, architects, SysOps professionals, business lea" data-next-head=""/><meta property="og:url" content="https://www.meetup.com/aws-user-group-lancashire/" data-next-head=""/><meta property="og:image" content="https://secure.meetupstatic.com/photos/event/b/6/f/2/600_525286834.jpeg" data-next-head=""/><meta property="al:android:app_name" content="Meetup" data-next-head=""/><meta property="al:android:package" content="com.meetup" data-next-head=""/><meta property="al:ios:app_store_id" content="375990038" data-next-head=""/><meta property="al:ios:app_name" content="Meetup" data-next-head=""/><meta property="al:web:should_fallback" content="true" data-next-head=""/><meta property="al:android:url" content="meetup://" data-next-head=""/><meta property="al:ios:url" content="meetup://" data-next-head=""/><meta property="al:web:url" content="https://www.meetup.com/" data-next-head=""/><meta property="twitter:card" content="summary_large_image" data-next-head=""/><meta property="twitter:site" content="@meetup" data-next-head=""/><meta property="twitter:image" content="https://secure.meetupstatic.com/photos/event/b/6/f/2/600_525286834.jpeg" data-next-head=""/><meta property="twitter:description" content="Welcome to AWS User Group Lancashire! This community welcomes anyone enthusiastic about Amazon Web Services (AWS), cloud computing or technology in general, whether you&#x27;re an experienced user or just starting out.Our aim is to bring together developers, architects, SysOps professionals, business lea" data-next-head=""/><meta property="twitter:app:id:iphone" content="375990038" data-next-head=""/><meta property="twitter:app:name:iphone" content="Meetup" data-next-head=""/><meta property="twitter:app:id:ipad" content="375990038" data-next-head=""/><meta property="twitter:app:name:ipad" content="Meetup" data-next-head=""/><meta property="twitter:app:id:googleplay" content="com.meetup" data-next-head=""/><meta property="twitter:app:name:googleplay" content="Meetup" data-next-head=""/><meta name="robots" content="index, follow, max-image-preview:large" data-next-head=""/><script type="application/ld+json" data-next-head="">[{"@context":"https://schema.org","@type":"Event","name":"AWS UG Lancashire x Rossendale Digital June 2026: Rossendale","url":"https://www.meetup.com/aws-user-group-lancashire/events/314993875/","description":"**AWS User Group Lancashire** comes to Rossendale! We are joining **Rossendale Digital** to support a digital hub so that residents can benefit from a programme of skills and events whilst businesses can share their knowledge and experience with each other.\n\n**\\|\\|\\| FEATURED TALKS \\|\\|\\|**\n\n🎙️**[Damien Jones](https://www.linkedin.com/in/mrdamienjones/) \\- AWS Consultant @ [Steamhaus](https://www.steamhaus.co.uk/)**\n\n***\"Best in Show: Building a Crufts-Ready AWS Business Platform in 5 Weeks\"***\n\nA new dog training business is launched. You have 5 weeks to develop a new production-ready platform before Crufts: the world's biggest dog show. Could you deliver?\n\nIn this talk, I'll share the real-world journey of building WolfieAndFriends on AWS. We'll review my architectural choices, \"build vs buy\" decisions and the trade-offs made during those hectic early days. You'll learn how to use AWS serverless, IaC and AI services to enable rapid delivery, shorten development times and transform a greenfield project into a professional, scalable platform that pays the bills.\n\nWhether you're a startup founder or an enterprise dev, you'll walk away with a blueprint for rapid delivery without sacrificing long-term stability. Expect Amplify, CDK, Q Developer, Kiro and more!\n\nThere will be a chance to network🗣️ and of course the obligatory 🍕on offer.\nGrab your space!\n\n**\\|\\|\\| SCHEDULE \\|\\|\\|**\n17:00 - Doors\n17:30 - Speaker\n18:00 - Refreshments & networking\n18:20 - Live exploration of Kiro\n19:00 - Close\n\n**\\|\\|\\| LOCATION & HOW TO FIND US \\|\\|\\|**\nThe Old Milk Depot, Bacup Road, Rawtenstall, Lancashire, BB4 7FE\n\nThe Old Milk Depot is a 10 minute walk from Rawtenstall town centre, with free on-site parking for easy access.\n\nWhat3words - [https://w3w.co/artist.leader.best](https://w3w.co/artist.leader.best)\nGoogle Pin - [https://maps.app.goo.gl/vHaDVoRvmj3bvL1d9](https://maps.app.goo.gl/vHaDVoRvmj3bvL1d9)\n\n**\\|\\|\\| SPONSORS \\|\\|\\|**\nAWS User Group Lancashire thanks our generous sponsors:\n\n* [Innovate Lancashire](https://innovatelancashire.co.uk/)\n* [Lancashire Digital Hub](https://lancashiredigitalhub.co.uk/)\n* [Rossendale Borough Council](https://www.rossendale.gov.uk/)\n* [Northern Reach](https://northernreach.co.uk/)","startDate":"2026-06-24T16:00:00.000Z","endDate":"2026-06-24T18:00:00.000Z","eventStatus":"https://schema.org/EventScheduled","image":"","eventAttendanceMode":"https://schema.org/OfflineEventAttendanceMode","location":{"@type":"Place","name":"Old Milk Depot","address":{"@type":"PostalAddress","addressLocality":"Rawtenstall","addressRegion":"","addressCountry":"gb","streetAddress":"The Old Milk Depot, Bacup Road, Rawtenstall, Lancashire, BB4 7FE, Rawtenstall"}},"organizer":{"@type":"Organization","name":"AWS User Group Lancashire","url":"https://www.meetup.com/aws-user-group-lancashire/"},"performer":"AWS User Group Lancashire"}]</script><script type="application/ld+json" data-next-head="">{"@type":"Organization","@context":"https://schema.org","url":"https://www.meetup.com/aws-user-group-lancashire/","name":"AWS User Group Lancashire","image":"https://secure.meetupstatic.com/photos/event/b/6/f/2/600_525286834.webp","foundingDate":"2024-12-18T14:33:54.000Z","address":{"location":{"@type":"Place","address":{"@type":"PostalAddress","addressLocality":"Burnley","addressRegion":"H2","addressCountry":"gb"}}},"sameAs":["https://www.linkedin.com/company/aws-user-group-lancashire","https://gravatar.com/awsuglancs"]}</script><script type="application/ld+json" data-next-head="">{"@context":"https://schema.org","@type":"BreadcrumbList","itemListElement":[{"@type":"ListItem","position":1,"item":{"@id":"https://www.meetup.com/aws-user-group-lancashire/","name":"AWS User Group Lancashire"}}]}</script><meta property="geo.position" content="53.8;-2.26" data-next-head=""/><meta property="geo.placename" content